'''瑞典駐越南大使館'''（{{lang-sv|Sveriges ambassad i Hanoi}}；{{vie|v=Đại sứ quán Thụy Điển tại Việt Nam|hn=大使館瑞典在越南|f=y}}）是[[瑞典王國|瑞典王國]]對[[越南社會主義共和國|越南社會主義共和國]]設置的[[瑞典駐外機構列表|外交代表機構]]，館址位於[[河內市|河內市]][[巴亭郡|巴亭郡]]竹山街2號（{{lang|vi|Số 2 Núi Trúc Quận Ba Đình}}）<ref name="地址">{{Cite web|language=vi |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/vi-VN/Embassies/Hanoi/Lien-h/i-s-quan-va-Lanh-s-quan/ |script-title=vi:Đại sứ quán và Lãnh sự quán |publisher={{lang|vi| Đại sứ quán Thụy Điển tại Hà Nội}} |accessdate=2016-02-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822225106/http://www.swedenabroad.com/vi-VN/Embassies/Hanoi/Lien-h/i-s-quan-va-Lanh-s-quan/ |archivedate=2015-08-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。瑞典駐越大使館是最早於越南前身國家——[[越南民主共和國|越南民主共和國]]（北越）設立的西方大使館之一，自1970年開始運作，1980年後則遷入第二代新館辦公，並以瑞越兩國間的雙邊關係為職責。

==歷史==
瑞典在[[冷戰|冷戰]]時期曾與[[越南共和國|越南共和國]]（南越）建交，但由[[曼谷|曼谷]]的{{Link-sv|瑞典駐泰國大使館|Sveriges ambassad i Bangkok}}兼當駐南越代表處。1967年4月17日時，瑞典政府宣布裁減對越代表團的規模，取消了駐泰大使館兼轄涉越事務的機能，改由其設於南越首都西貢（今[[胡志明市|胡志明市]]）的[[名譽領事|名譽領事]]館以维持瑞典与南越的双边关系<ref name="Search">{{lang|en|{{Cite book |language=en |title=The Search for Peace in Vietnam, 1964-1968 |author=Gardner, Lloyd C.|publisher={{Link-en|德克薩斯州農工大學出版社|Texas A&M University Press|Texas A&M University Press}} |isbn= 9781603446501|date=2004|page=p. 193}}}}</ref>。在瑞典與南越斷交1年多之後的1969年1月10日，[[瑞典首相|瑞典首相]][[塔格·埃蘭德|塔格·埃蘭德]]正式宣告承認北越<ref name="紀">{{lang|en|{{Cite news |language=en |title=Sweden to Establish Ties With North Viet Regime|publisher={{Link-en|紀錄衛報|The Register-Guard|Eugene Register-Guard}} |date= 1969-01-10 |page=p. 2A}}}}</ref>，翌日兩國締結邦交，瑞典遂成為最早承認河內政府的西方國家<ref name="越外">{{Cite web |language=en |script-title=en:Overview of Vietnam-Sweden Relations |date=2007 |publisher={{lang|en|{{Link-en|越南外交部|Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Vietnam)|Press and Information Department, Vietnam Ministry of Foreign Affairs}} }} |url=http://www.vietnamembassy-brunei.org/vnemb.vn/cn_vakv/euro/nr040819111931/ns071211135922 |accessdate=2016-02-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20160224161427/http://www.vietnamembassy-brunei.org/vnemb.vn/cn_vakv/euro/nr040819111931/ns071211135922 |archivedate=2016-02-24 }}</ref>。

瑞越建交之初曾暫時以[[北京|北京]]的[[瑞典駐華大使館|瑞典駐華大使館]]作為對越聯絡機構<ref name="紀"></ref>。1970年6月，河內的新瑞典大使館正式開館<ref name="越外"></ref>，最早的辦事處址設於北越政府用以接待外國元首、閣揆及使節的[[河內索菲特大都市飯店|大都會飯店]]105室<ref name="飯店">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Swedish brass plaque inaugurated at Metropole Hotel Hanoi |date=2015-12-06|author={{lang|en|Persson, Joakim}}|publisher={{lang|en|ScandAsia}} |url=http://scandasia.com/swedish-brass-plaque-inaugurated-at-metropole-hotel-hanoi/ |accessdate=2016-02-24 |archivedate= 2015-12-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212213142/http://scandasia.com/swedish-brass-plaque-inaugurated-at-metropole-hotel-hanoi/}}</ref>。1975年春，瑞典替佔地9,500[[平方公尺|平方公尺]]的大使館現址用地簽了60年份的租約，但由於河內市區的地質由[[紅河|紅河]]沖積而成，因此該塊地皮需先行實施排水作業及加固工程，才於1977年開始在其上興建館舍，由建築師{{Link-sv|貝蒂爾·福爾克|Bertil Falck}}操刀設計，於1980年落成啟用<ref name="sfv">{{Cite web |language=en |url=http://www-test.sfv.se/en/fastigheter/utrikes/asien/the-swedish-embassy-compound-in-hanoi-vietnam/ |publisher={{lang|en|{{Link-sv|瑞典國家資產局|Statens fastighetsverk|Statens fastighetsverk}}}} |access-date=2016-02-25 |archiveurl= http://archive.is/bNGmJ |archive-date=2016-02-24 |dead-url=yes  |script-title=en:The Swedish Embassy Compound in Hanoi, Vietnam }}</ref>。

2010年12月23日，瑞典駐越南使館在[[瑞典國會|瑞典國會]]決定把資助政府辦公處所的費用削減3億[[瑞典克朗|克朗]]之後，宣布其將與{{Link-sv|瑞典駐阿根廷大使館|Sveriges ambassad i Buenos Aires|駐阿根廷使館}}、{{Link-sv|瑞典駐比利時大使館|Sveriges ambassad i Bryssel|駐比利時使館}}、{{Link-sv|瑞典駐馬來西亞大使館|Sveriges ambassad i Kuala Lumpur|駐馬來西亞使館}}和駐[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]使館一起從2011年開始停止運作<ref name="青年報">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Budget cuts force Sweden to shut Vietnam embassy |date=2011-12-24 |publisher={{lang|en| {{Link-vi|越南青年報|Thanh Niên (báo)|Thanh Nien News}} }}|url=http://www.thanhniennews.com/politics/budget-cuts-force-sweden-to-shut-vietnam-embassy-13814.html |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2016-02-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225104720/http://www.thanhniennews.com/politics/budget-cuts-force-sweden-to-shut-vietnam-embassy-13814.html }}</ref>，而瑞方於閉館後仍透過駐泰大使館等渠道負責對越外交，並與河內和胡志明市的兩處瑞典駐越名譽領事機構合作<ref name="繼續">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Sweden-Vietnam Diplomatic Relations to be Continued |date=2011-06-03|author={{lang|en|Wildau, Bjarne}}|publisher={{lang|en|ScandAsia}} |url=http://scandasia.com/8992-sweden-vietnam-diplomatic-relations-to-be-continued/ |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2016-02-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224142421/http://scandasia.com/8992-sweden-vietnam-diplomatic-relations-to-be-continued/}}</ref>。同年9月6日，瑞典隨著該國最大在野黨——[[瑞典社會民主工人黨|社會民主黨]]與執政當局就政府辦公處所預算一事達成協議，而重新開放駐越大使館等遭到關閉的駐外機構<ref name="重開">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:The Embassy of Sweden in Hanoi continues to operate |date=2011-09-06|publisher={{lang|en|Embassy of Sweden, Hanoi}} |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Current-affairs/News/The-Embassy-of-Sweden-in-Hanoi-continues-to-operate/ |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2016-02-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225103421/http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Current-affairs/News/The-Embassy-of-Sweden-in-Hanoi-continues-to-operate/}}</ref>。

==組織與執掌==
瑞典駐越南大使館的任務是瑞越關係的強化及協助雙邊政府、企業、組織合作，同時也替瑞典在越僑民、遊客及越南赴瑞人士提供領事或移民服務<ref name="簡">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:About the Embassy |publisher={{lang|en|Embassy of Sweden, Hanoi}} |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/About-us/About-the-Embassy/ |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2015-07-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707125400/http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/About-us/About-the-Embassy/}}</ref>。館內下轄部門包括行政領事處<ref name="員">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Embassy Staff |publisher={{lang|en|Embassy of Sweden, Hanoi}} |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/About-us/Embassy-Staff/ |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2015-01-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124095220/http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/About-us/Embassy-Staff/}}</ref>、政治貿易處和商務處（{{Link-sv|瑞典貿易投資委員會|Business Sweden}}駐越機構）等科組<ref name="商貿">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Trade between Sweden and Vietnam |publisher={{lang|en|Embassy of Sweden, Hanoi}} |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Business/Trade-with-Sweden/ |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2016-01-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126234348/http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Business/Trade-with-Sweden/}}</ref>，大使以下的館員則有[[使領館副館長|副館長]]、秘書官及數位越南籍雇員，分管媒體通信、文化、旅遊、金融等領域的館務<ref name="員"></ref>。位於胡志明市[[胡志明市第二郡|第二郡]]{{Link-vi|草田坊|Thảo Điền}}阮文享街186號（{{lang|vi|186 Nguyễn Văn Hưởng}}）的名譽總領事館則負責受理、申辦越南南部諸省的特定領事業務<ref name="HCMC">{{Cite web|language=en |script-title=en:Swedish consulates - Ho Chi Minh City |publisher={{lang|en|Embassy of Sweden, Hanoi}} |url=http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Contact/Embassy--Consulates/#HoChiMinhCity |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archivedate= 2016-01-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123052746/http://www.swedenabroad.com/en-GB/Embassies/Hanoi/Contact/Embassy--Consulates/#HoChiMinhCity}}</ref>。

